r-kafka:5.0.1/e8f23613392c9ed17ea039ddc1bae284.out\n../7031-83b3a4c4/build/tests/org.springframework.cloud:spring-cloud-stream-binder-kafka:5.0.1/b31f3d794fb8cde38946158bd38560bd.out\n../7031-83b3a4c4/build/tests/org.springframework.cloud:spring-cloud-stream-binder-kafka:5.0.1/47eafa91b2255ae2226b0845432b8a9b.out\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
